Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the iconic show "The Most Useful\NSchool in the World" from Nichiuri TV .
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle was scheduled to make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While visiting the TV station where\Nthe filming would take place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prominent enka singer, Kimijima Noburou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwho was also appearing on the same show...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Showed off his proud vase to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the appraisal of his vase was\Nto be conducted during the show...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it was valued at over 100 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, that vase suddenly disappeared during the rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that someone stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that was the case, the culprit would have to be in this studio...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like fog clearing up in a swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see through both romance and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surfacing from that popular show is the\Nmystery of the sudden missing vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you hear me out, Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the beginning of the rehearsal, I\Nhaven't stepped out of the studio at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, not just Principal Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the rehearsal, no one carried any personal belongings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Large enough to tuck a vase in, out the studio if I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:17.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kamisuwa Mikihiko (52)\NNichiuri TV Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's split up and search\Ncarefully in the studio one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsuchiya Daisuke (45)\NDirector
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it really just vanished like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's a magic vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way it could have vanished on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:48.61,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kimijima Noburou (67)\NLeading Figure in Enka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a vase from the Qing Dynasty with\Nan estimated value of 100 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone got dazzled by its worth and hid it\Naway with the intent to steal it, no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, we can't be sure about that at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sudden disappearance of an item...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, last week Takikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}\Nconducted an interesting experiment in his lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fake flower placed on top of a pot filled with rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disappeared all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth was, a hose was inserted from underneath the flower pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When air was pumped out from it, the rice\Ngrains about floated with a swoosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The force supporting the flower plummeted in an instant,\Ncausing the fake flower to sink into the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it looked as if it disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that trick is not applicable to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, someone among us has to be the offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a request, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once and for all, can we rely on the great detective\NMouri Kogorou's deductions to flush out the vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please kindly lend us your strength again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} can find the vase without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The great detective Mouri Kogorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall definitely recover Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nvase for you to see without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will Dad be all right after blowing up a huge balloon of confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, guess the show's on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, according to the testimony of the\Nassistant director Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:23.83,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto Yoshinari (22)\NAssistant Director
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up until the rehearsal for first period was concluded...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The vase was definitely still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I was checking the props.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I also witnessed the vase at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That said, if we assume somebody did steal that vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would've had to do it during the second period rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were paying full attention to the\Npuffed rice maker, they seized the opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stole Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s vase, and hid it\Nsomewhere in this studio as quick as a wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, we've searched high and low\Njust now and still couldn't find the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is still a place we haven't searched yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:05.46,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki Tetsushi (32)\NPuffed Rice Maker Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding that puffed rice maker case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the one who checked its content, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we won't find Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s vase inside that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you suspecting me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During my rehearsal for the first period, when\Nyou were taking secret pictures of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a fan of Ydko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, so I couldn't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're a fan, watch your manners all the more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, furious at your taking pictures\Nof Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snapped your cell phone in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:07:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holding a grudge against him for that, you went ahead and stole\NKimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s vase in order to get back at him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you say so, why not show us what's inside your case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was testing my puffed rice maker,\NI remained in the set the entire time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How on earth did I have the time to steal the vase!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's precisely where the blind spot is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, I believe nobody kept their\Neyes on Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why didn't he do the hammering\Nhimself instead of asking Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's eyes were fixed on the puffed rice maker in that instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, I believe no one was able to\Nwitness Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just your assumption!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why I did the hammering...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because it was written on the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, wise up, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we've been telling you to at least read the script!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took photos of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwithout permission left a bad impression on you, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you jumped into conclusions, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not as narrow-minded a man as you may think!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man is definitely hiding something from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I shouldn't be surprised that Uncle noticed it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we should be able to find\Nout once we see the inside of that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to ask this, but could you let us take\Na look inside your case as a precaution?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you care to explain what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My impulses got the best of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was indeed as Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said, I was furious\Nbecause my cell phone was snapped into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a grown man, how insolent of you\Nto take peeping photos of an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to go and break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screw it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed the handkerchief Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was using fell on the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought if I auctioned off the handkerchief and a\Nphoto of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} using it as a set over the internet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could maybe sell it for a high price to fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screwing around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, wasn't the photo in question unusable since it was\Ndestroyed by Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} along with the cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he set it so that photos will be saved in a microSD card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By doing this, his photos will remain\Nintact even if the cell phone is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a problem too, but for now we\Nneed to focus on Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where on earth did it vanish to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:18.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Honma Kentarou (70)\NAntique Appraiser
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing's the matter, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If problems keep surfacing like that, I'm sure\Nthe filming for today is called off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we haven't decided on doing that just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a busy schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies, but before you leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind showing us the contents of that large baggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were pretty intrigued by that vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remarkable...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see it caught your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, during the puffed rice maker demo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you leave the set all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I'm the culprit just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I merely think it's possible to conceal a vase\Nin baggage like that and nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My vase is not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for doubting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's true that if one carries such large baggage\Nout of the studio, suspicion will surely ensue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't give it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold on, Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What else do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like we have decided to terminate our filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s second period lecture for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for your third period lecture, Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we recover Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s lost vase, we\Nwill still continue filming as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, may I ask you not to go home just yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you do manage to find the vase, I\Ndoubt you'll be able to continue filming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You won't be able to film even if the vase is found"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this Sensei know something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamisuwa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, we're already fairly behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is among us, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, show yourself and return my vase at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Barring Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody in this studio has personal belongings large\Nenough to conceal your vase, Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then where the heck is my vase now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that no one carried a container out of\Nthe studio big enough to conceal the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having said that, we did search everywhere\Nin the studio but failed to locate the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But of course it couldn't have gone with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I definitely missed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's call it a day and stop our filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for today's filming, we'll call it a day here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the art staff members please disassemble the set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dissemble... the set?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto, lend me your cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, isn't it about time you got sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still haven't located the vase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting sleepy is not -
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or I shouldn't do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monkey see monkey do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to deal not with the set...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the case first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, do you know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whereabouts of the vase too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the Sleeping Kogorou's famous deduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shall see its true worth with our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit still has the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit still has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Still has it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all of here are empty-handed, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closely, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among us, two people are wearing waist bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the staff said they were disassembling the set earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I confirmed the insides of assistant\Ndirector Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please check it however you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only have these things in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only you left, Oki Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That vase from the Qing Dynasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could never fit into such a small waist bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's more than possible if one shatters the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The vase was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shattered?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Qing vase valued at 100 million yen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if the vase was shattered, wouldn't\Neveryone immediately notice the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody was able to notice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please recall what happened during\Nthe rehearsal for the second period lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When all of us were focusing on the\Ntesting of the puffed rice machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You secretly went through the back of the set...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put the vase in a bag you prepared\Nbeforehand so that the shards wouldn't scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} used the hammer to bang on the puffed rice maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, here comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shattered the vase from outside the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, you stuffed your waist pouch with a bagful of vase shards...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And reappeared at the scene like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She took advantage of the loud puffed rice maker\Nnoise to cover the sound of the shattering vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were always yelling at her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I bet she hated you for that, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever hatred she might have had...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't believe someone in their right\Nmind would smash a 100 million yen vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just goes to show how much she despises him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have one more thing I'd like to ask Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding the appraisal result of that vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to reveal that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't seem she wishes for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if this keeps up, Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will be made into a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that her choice as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how the results may be against Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the subject of the Qing vase in\NMr. Kimijima Noburou's possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I deem it a remarkable counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That vase was a counterfeit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, earlier today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite a work of art, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'll allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remarkable...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You meant to say "it's a remarkable fake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, you have seen through its fakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were to declare it a fake during filming,\NKimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would lose face as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having that said, I cannot lie about my appraisal results.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Troubled by this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tried to leave the scene without a word before filming but failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid she had the same feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knowing how deeply on Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is of his vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't bring yourself to let out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In comes the invitation to be on the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the appraisal were to take place in the\Nshow, it would be revealed that it is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simply because you didn't break the news up to this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your master was about to lose face on national television.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Worrying yourself over this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You decided to make it look like a vase theft...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to halt the filming, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, exactly as you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the vase was a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year ago, before your wife passed\Naway, she called me to her bedside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although that vase is a fake, it's still\Nan irreplaceable treasure to Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"So I would like you to keep Sensei from\Nfinding out at all costs," she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since I couldn't keep the promise\Nand things turned out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am unable to remain by your side, Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this, I will hang up my hat, give\Nup my singer dream and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for all these years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do not embarrass me any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that my eye for vases is gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe my discerning eye for singers is unclouded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I received a call along with a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your debut has been approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the producer was rather indecisive...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went ahead and gave him an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make me repeat myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said there's nothing to worry about, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fiddlesticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you can't trust my judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oki Shinobu is the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have my guarantee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you still plan to go home despite all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:55.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,THE MOST USEFUL SCHOOL IN THE WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've somehow solved another case, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good, I can't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention, but your necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you've indeed noticed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wore this just to attract your attention, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Has gravy from your boxed lunch on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gravely in shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even a necktie can't save...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His neck from embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.57,0:24:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case is she really that real estate king...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Katayose Ouzaburou's granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.37,0:24:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That freak car was your doing, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The garden fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You put a hole in it, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did the culprit disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.32,0:24:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SOLVING MYSTERIES AT THE RED LEAF PALACE\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.51,0:24:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Milk Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.71,0:24:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Friday (Nov. 25) is a broadcast of the movie "The Raven Chaser"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.52,0:24:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch it at home!
